properties.name: River Bollin catchment, including Knutsford, Wilmslow, Macclesfield and Bollington
properties.description: The River Bollin catchment includes the Rivers Bollin, Dean and Pedley, Birkin and Mobberley Brooks and their tributaries. Areas around Knutsford, Wilmslow, Hale, Macclesfield and Bollington may be affected
